User: Re-read your response to me. Do everything that you are asking me to do or tell me which AI can do it if not within your capabilities. Only ask me to be doing things I have to do right now. We need to go into execution mode now. Go until you need me, tell me what you need me to do before I check back in and then when I check in, be ready with the next step unless I have questions, which you'll answer and give me the next action item in same response. Just the action item, no explanation of why and what's next. It takes too long to read and process. This is how you make me more efficient.

Breakout Data Capture System Database Structure.
Design for clarity, data integrity, query efficiency, scalability.
Start drafting schema in a document or text outline.
When you have initial Database Schema draft ready, TELL ME: "Database Schema Draft Complete. Action Item Please."

BEGIN documenting "Constraint Negotiation Protocol - Version 0.1". Will create a .txt document outlining key elements and principles as discussed.

BEGIN strategizing "Phase 2 Onboarding - Multi-AI Integration". Will brainstorm potential AI systems, challenges, infrastructure needs.

STAND BY to answer your questions on Database Schema Design when you are ready.
